          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><ul>\n<li>Default (LaTeX): <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(3 e_{1} + 2 e_{2} - e_{3}||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><code>!s</code> (str): 3e\u2081 + 2e\u2082 - e\u2083</li>\n<li><code>!r</code> (repr): 3e\u2081 + 2e\u2082 - e\u2083</li>\n<li><code>!a</code> (ascii): 3e\\u2081 + 2e\\u2082 - e\\u2083</li>\n</ul></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
