            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"explicit-wrappers\">Explicit Wrappers</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Use <code>gm.latex()</code>, <code>gm.block_latex()</code>, and <code>gm.text()</code> to override\nauto-detection when needed.</span></span>"
