            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"basis-vector-properties\">Basis Vector Properties</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>e\u2081</strong>: <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(e_{1}||)</marimo-tex>, square = <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(1||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><strong>e\u2082</strong>: <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(e_{2}||)</marimo-tex>, square = <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(1||)</marimo-tex></li>\n<li><strong>e\u2083</strong>: <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(e_{3}||)</marimo-tex>, square = <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(1||)</marimo-tex></li>\n</ul>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">All basis vectors square to <marimo-tex class=\"arithmatex\">||(+1||)</marimo-tex> \u2713</span></span>"
